title: MisterMusic Show 323 - indie,alternative,rock radio
description:
MisterMusic Show 323   - [120 minutes] 192 kbps MP3 -



It's a 2 hour mix focusing heavily on indie, alternative tunes , with a couple classic hits from the past thrown in to make a lively show.

The 'Oldie of the Week' topped the US modern rock charts in September 1993.  It also made a comeback to the number 1 slot a couple weeks later in October that year. It is one of the better known alternative music hits of the early nineties.


The MisterMusic Show is broadcast weekly and heard globally on RockXS internet radio.
